PyAST is a Python3 extension that provides an interface
to the Starlink AST library. It can be obtained from
https://github.com/timj/starlink-pyast/downloads. To
install, do:

python3 setup.py install

or

python3 setup.py install --prefix=<installation directory>

To test it, do:

python3 starlink/ast/test/test.py

To view documentation, open pyast.htx/pyast.html in
your favourite browser, or view the docs online at
http://dsberry.github.com/starlink/pyast.html



